title: Medieval Warfare Volume VI, Issue 5
description:
Medieval Warfare Magazine 

Volume VI, Issue 5 - The Knights Templar

A bi-monthly magazine that examines the military history of Medieval Europe and the Middle-East, from ca. AD 500 to 1500. Each issue is focused around a unique theme and richly illustrated with custom artwork and photographs.

Subscriptions from the content creator can be made here: https://www.karwansaraypublishers.com/shop/medieval-warfare/subscriptions.html?
